<span id="freeTextContainer5625287171088157477">The Chronicles of Avonlea centres around all the people who were in Avonlea during the time when Anne came to Green Gables. <br/><br/>There are twelve chapters and each chapter is a short story about one, or a group of people. Anne does make a cameo appearance in a few of the chapters. <br/><br/>I&apos;m not a fan of short stories and I did struggle to stay interested however with just one book to go I&apos;m determined to read every book Anne has featured in. <br/><br/>The finishing line is looming.</span>
