<span id="freeTextContainer6342837152229212566">This is a lovely book of short stories, each of which is a gem. The first time I read it I wasn&apos;t very impressed, but this second reading has revealed to me the beauty, depth, and wonderful messages that are always present in LMM&apos;s work. She expresses human emotions and desires so poignantly.<br/><br/>I love how each story is multi-faceted. There&apos;s something to learn from each character. I know I will revisit this book again and again!</span>
  <span id="freeText6342837152229212566" style="display:none">This is a lovely book of short stories, each of which is a gem. The first time I read it I wasn't very impressed, but this second reading has revealed to me the beauty, depth, and wonderful messages that are always present in LMM's work. She expresses human emotions and desires so poignantly.<br /><br />I love how each story is multi-faceted. There's something to learn from each character. I know I will revisit this book again and again!</span>
