<span id="freeTextContainer4676475342231776020">If you&apos;re picking this up expecting more Anne then you&apos;re going to be sorely disappointed. Anne makes a really brief cameo in the first story, and is mentioned in 3 or 4 others (very briefly). If you&apos;re looking for a collection of short stories that sheds some light on habitants of Avonlea that don&apos;t get talked about much in the Anne series then you&apos;re in for a good time. This is a very sweet collection of short stories, majority of which focus on romance.</span>
  <span id="freeText4676475342231776020" style="display:none">If you're picking this up expecting more Anne then you're going to be sorely disappointed. Anne makes a really brief cameo in the first story, and is mentioned in 3 or 4 others (very briefly). If you're looking for a collection of short stories that sheds some light on habitants of Avonlea that don't get talked about much in the Anne series then you're in for a good time. This is a very sweet collection of short stories, majority of which focus on romance.</span>
